*----------------------------
* 1) Import excel dataset and cleaning
*----------------------------
*--------------------------------------------------
* Description
*--------------------------------------------------
/*
This do-files cleans household surveys conducted in Bangladesh in 2018.

 1) Initial changes (dropping empty variables and renaming some variables)
 2) Labeling
 3) Setup variables (dates, location where data was gathered, ... )
 4) Socio-economic variables (age, gender, income, assets, ...)
 5) Priming (priming check variables)
 6) Confirmation bias
 7) Climate change (perception of CC, experiences, ...)
 8) Migration (migration preferences, plans, and experiences)
 9) Preferences (time & risk preferences, place attachment, ...)
 10) Network (number of friends and how they are connected with each other)

*/
*--------------------------------------------------


clear all
insheet using "$working_ANALYSIS\data\bangladesh2018.csv", delimiter(";") clear

*--------------------------------------------------
* 1) Initial changes
{
*dropping variables that were necessary for programing only
drop location_note treatment_emotions_note dg_note migration_temp_note migration_temp_note_001 migration_reasons_note migration_reasons_ranking_note mp_note1 mp_note2 migration_abroad_note mc_note mr_note migration_success_note attitudes_note contact_note cc_resettle_note cc_conspiracy_note erosion_note_a erosion_explaination_note_a erosion_animation_note_a accretion_note_a accretion_explaination_note_a accretion_video_note_a accretion_note_b accretion_explaination_note_b accretion_video_note_b erosion_note_b erosion_explaination_note_b erosion_animation_note_b friends_names_note friends_characteristics_note intro_livestock_note intro_immovables_note intro_movables_note thanks_note payout_dg_note payout_spite_note1 payout_spite_note2
drop intro_living intro_living_prev intro_home treatment_emotions_intro dg_intro_0 dg_intro spite_intro risk_intro_0 risk_intro t_intro intro_willingness intro_faith_government intro_ccperception intro_expectation intro_trust_information intro_cc_contribution info_placeattachment  _uuid _id assistant_notes

*Dropping empty variables
drop religion_other t0_video t1_video payout_risk_a payout_risk_b payout_risk_c

rename marital_status marital
rename years_schooling edu
rename living_forever village_same
rename uncertain_times c1a
rename easy_relax c1b
rename fatalism c1c
rename optimism c1d
rename friends c1e
rename keep_busy c1f
rename pessimism c1g
rename upset c1h
rename fatalism2 c1i
rename optimism2 c1j
rename participation_community_activiti comunity_activities
rename _index _id
rename migration_temp_place_001 migration_perm_place
rename migration_temp_divison_001 migration_perm_divison
rename migration_temp_distance_001 migration_perm_distance
}
